config XIAOMI_MIGT
	tristate "Xiaomi MIGT performance framework"
	help
	  Xiaomi MIGT is a vendor performance framework used for frame-aware
	  boosting, game/load classification, FLT/GLK tuning, and related
	  scheduler hooks.

	  This is a reverse-engineered compatibility layer. Enable it only if
	  your tree also provides the Xiaomi WALT/Metis/MIST hook surface or the
	  matching companion modules.

